response:
To fulfill your request, I will create a VPC with an Internet Gateway for public connectivity, three subnets (one public, two private), and a NAT Gateway (optional but recommended for private subnet internet access, omitted here for simplicity unless requested). We will then deploy the Web EC2 instance, the App EC2 instance, and the RDS instance with appropriate Security Groups to ensure the Web server can talk to the App server, and the App server can talk to the Database.

