3. `aws_lightsail_disk_attachment`: The resource that links the disk to the instance.

The following configuration demonstrates this setup in the `us-east-1` region.

```hcl
# Configure the AWS Provider
provider "aws" {
  region = "us-east-1"
}

# 1. Create a Lightsail Instance
resource "aws_lightsail_instance" "example_server" {
  name              = "example-instance"
  availability_zone = "us-east-1a"
